title: Cam Newton out for year, Nick Foles will start for Jags in Week 11 - Emergency Podcast (Football 11/5)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Ryan Wilson, John Breech and Sean Wagner-McGough to react to breaking news that the Panthers have placed Cam Newton on injured reserve (1:15). The guys answer if Newton has played his final game in a Carolina uniform and what could transpire with his contract this offseason. Will, Ryan, John and Sean also discuss the Jaguars decision to go back to Nick Foles at QB after their Week 10 bye (19:45) as well as adamant comments from the Chargers' owner that they won't be moving to London (27:45).
